MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b99f5871884a9d74d9c948daa04e503a, type: 3}
  m_Name: FeedbackData
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FeedbackData
  stsPositivePool:
  - Your mind was clear. The battlefield had no hold on you.
  - Exceptional mental resource management; your cognitive shield was virtually impenetrable.
  - Solid focus through critical moments; your stress management was quite satisfactory.
  - Consistent distraction filtering; you effectively recovered your flow state at
    a steady rhythm.
  - 'Focus capacity consistent with modern norms; your attention was adequate for
    baseline performance.  '
  - Standard concentration levels achieved; you maintained momentum despite occasional
    lapses.
  stsNegativePool:
  - When it peaks, stop moving. Let it settle
  - Hold your ground. Sprinting feeds the stress
  - External stimuli are beginning to impact your focus; try a steadier rhythm to
    lower your stress.
  - Minor fluctuations in mental stability detected; a brief reset may improve your
    next performance.
  - 'High stress is making your character fragile; you are taking extra damage because
    your mind is absent. '
  - Your mind is too fragmented to survive; cease impulsive actions and regain self-control
    immediately.
  timePositivePool:
  - Efficient. Precise. You wasted nothing.
  - 'Moved with absolute purpose and speed; zero time was wasted on irrelevant stimuli. '
  - 'Clear time reflects high efficiency; you managed all objectives systematically
    and swiftly. '
  - Time management is well above average; your progression remained steady throughout
    the mission.
  - Operational speed is typical for the digital age; objectives were cleared within
    standard parameters.
  - Baseline performance rhythm; you achieved the goal within the acceptable time
    window.
  timeNegativePool:
  - Move with purpose. Every extra second adds up
  - Dragging fights out costs more than losing them
  - Floor duration is becoming excessive; consider ignoring secondary tasks to protect
    your time resources.
  - Procrastination is causing tactical disadvantage; dithering at obstacles kills
    your focus momentum.
  - You are lingering on non-essentials for too long; every wasted second costs you
    survival odds.
  - Chronic delay is leading to failure; lingering on trivialities will result in
    immediate termination.
  rankDescriptions:
  - rankLetter: S
    description: Demonstrates outstanding mental resource management and maintains
      an exceptionally high level of concentration stability.
  - rankLetter: A
    description: Maintains consistent attentional control and exhibits rapid, systematic
      recovery of the flow state.
  - rankLetter: B
    description: Sustains a steady operational rhythm and manages cognitive focus
      effectively within standard performance benchmarks.
  - rankLetter: C
    description: Displays concentration levels typical of the digital era, with susceptibility
      to frequent environmental distractions.
  - rankLetter: D
    description: Shows persistent goal tracking despite fragile focus and high vulnerability
      to external stimuli.
